## 6. Data Deletion Requests (GDPR / CCPA)
The app itself does not collect personal data.  
For data that may be collected by third-party ad providers (e.g., Liftoff Monetize), you may request deletion by contacting us at **flirtyquizcontact@gmail.com**. We will forward your request to the relevant provider where applicable.

